#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.sort_values.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.sort\\_values"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_values.dataframe_sort_values:1 of
msgid "Sort by the values along either axis."
msgstr "按值沿任一轴排序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_values.dataframe_sort_values of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_values.dataframe_sort_values:3 of
msgid "Input dataframe."
msgstr "输入的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_values.dataframe_sort_values:5 of
msgid "Name or list of names to sort by."
msgstr "用于排序的列名或列名列表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_values.dataframe_sort_values:7 of
msgid "Axis to be sorted."
msgstr "要排序的轴。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_values.dataframe_sort_values:9 of
msgid ""
"Sort ascending vs. descending. Specify list for multiple sort orders.  If"
" this is a list of bools, must match the length of the by."
msgstr ""
"升序或降序排序。若指定多个排序顺序，请提供列表。如果这是一个布尔值列表，"
"则必须与 by 的长度一致。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_values.dataframe_sort_values:13 of
msgid "If True, perform operation in-place."
msgstr "如果为 True，则就地执行操作。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_values.dataframe_sort_values:15 of
msgid ""
"Choice of sorting algorithm. See also ndarray.np.sort for more "
"information.  `mergesort` is the only stable algorithm. For DataFrames, "
"this option is only applied when sorting on a single column or label."
msgstr ""
"排序算法的选择。更多信息请参见 ndarray.np.sort。`mergesort` 是唯一的稳定"
"算法。对于 DataFrame，此选项仅在按单个列或标签排序时应用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_values.dataframe_sort_values:20 of
msgid "Puts NaNs at the beginning if `first`; `last` puts NaNs at the end."
msgstr "如果为 `first`，则将 NaN 值放在开头；`last` 将 NaN 值放在结尾。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_values.dataframe_sort_values:23 of
msgid "If True, the resulting axis will be labeled 0, 1, …, n - 1."
msgstr "如果为 True，则结果轴的标签将为 0, 1, ..., n - 1。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_values.dataframe_sort_values:25 of
msgid ""
"Parallel sorting algorithm, for the details, refer to: "
"http://csweb.cs.wfu.edu/bigiron/LittleFE-"
"PSRS/build/html/PSRSalgorithm.html"
msgstr ""
"并行排序算法，详细信息请参考：http://csweb.cs.wfu.edu/bigiron/LittleFE-"
"PSRS/build/html/PSRSalgorithm.html"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_values.dataframe_sort_values of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_values.dataframe_sort_values:29 of
msgid ""
"**sorted_obj** -- DataFrame with sorted values if inplace=False, None "
"otherwise."
msgstr ""
"**sorted_obj** -- 如果 inplace=False，则返回按值排序的 DataFrame，否则"
"返回 None。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_values.dataframe_sort_values of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_values.dataframe_sort_values:33 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_values.dataframe_sort_values:49 of
msgid "Sort by col1"
msgstr "按 col1 排序"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_values.dataframe_sort_values:60 of
msgid "Sort by multiple columns"
msgstr "按多个列排序"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_values.dataframe_sort_values:71 of
msgid "Sort Descending"
msgstr "降序排序"

